<p>AFK Leveling using the Leech method is horribly bad for your casting and melee skills. As a Necro, you should pride yourself on having a maxed out Defense and Offense, and at least one melee ability (1hb, Piercing) maxed out. AFK leveling will give you problems later on, depending on what level you are doing it at. While I was soloing in Dulaks, I let a guildie Ranger group with me and leech xp, but this was at level 50 and she didn't gain a level, so no problems there. Doing this at level 18 or so in Paludal Caverns is probably not the wisest idea. <br /> <br />Plus, don't you want to be there when you ding? I for one still get a lot of pleasure out of shouting 'DING! 51!' or whatever level it happens to be...espescially when I ding off of a completed quest in the PoK and get people asking 'How are you Xping on PoK?' </p>
