<p>I used to play EQ years ago and i heard of necro AFK leveling. Back in the day pets used to aggro anything you aggro'd, anything you were kos to, the pet was kos to.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br /> <br />It used to be that a necro could FD and the pet would get aggro and kill stuff while you are afk, and at the very worst the pet dies and the necro is safe because he is FD. Of course this doesnt work now days because FD makes the pet poof after a few minutes and mobs dont aggro the pet anymore. <br /> <br />So maybe your necro friends were talking about this?</p>
